title: Tezos Japonica
description:
Japanese NFT Artist Network invites you to join our Tezos NFT Event #TezosJaponica from May 25th - 29th, 2022.
Anyone can create NFT art related to Japanese Culture - Anime, Manga, Games, Geisha, Samurai, Food, Fashion, etc... The art can be about anything fitting the theme!
Participants can mint them on Tezos NFT marketplaces of their choice and tag TezosJaponica at mint time. Edition: 5-55 • Price: 0.5-5 tez. • No limit on submissions.
